// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-0239 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: test | Level: high | ID: 9b499340-b75a-5376-87e9-34cb6559930c

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
